292
00:19:26,830 --> 00:19:31,500
♪Aku tak mau mendengar takdir♪

293
00:19:32,390 --> 00:19:37,560
♪Berusaha mencari kabarmu♪

294
00:19:40,730 --> 00:19:44,410
♪Hutan Pertarungan Bintang yang
